
                        The Amiga Demo List History

931023:	- First release, but it didn't go far.

931106: - First widespread release.
	- 254502 bytes.
	- 201 groups and 414 productions listed.

931129: - Major update.
	- 549538 bytes.
	- 541 groups and 1352 productions listed.
	- Released version now stripped of all "@remark"'s and dividing
	  lines to reduce filesize.  42729 bytes saved from this release
	  as a result.
	- Groups with 5 or more productions in the list are marked with
	  an asterix (*) from the main node, to easily locate the more
	  widely known and productive groups.  Is this a good idea?
	- Added History file to archive.  ;^)

940125:	- 622853 bytes.
	- 587 groups and 1482 productions listed.
	- Changed main node to show only first letter of group names,
	  as the number of group names was growing far too large.  Hopefully
	  this will make it easier to quickly locate a group.
	- Added "Notes on Compatibility" node.
	- Added The Party 93 competition results.

940227:	- 648297 bytes.
	- 594 groups and 1519 productions listed.
	- Added European Computer Conference 93 competition results.

940405: - 747028 bytes.
	- 631 groups and 1691 productions listed.
	- Added The Gathering 94 competition results.
	- Fixed all bad links!

940814: - 878587 bytes.
	- 660 groups and 1904 productions listed.
	- Added Assembly 94 information.

940821: - Interim release.
	- 881281 bytes.
	- 662 groups and 1908 productions listed.

950506	- Split the main file into 8 parts.
	- 1443307 total bytes,
	- 836 groups and 3219 productions.
	- Added Party 94 and Gathering 95 party results.
	- Much work was done on integrating the Aminet demo archives into
	  the list.
